divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside. At my Uncle's house. We had just gotten home from being with family. Both my uncle and I observed it. Saw what appeared to be a plane, but looked more star like and did not blink. Was orange colored and when it got far enough away, I saw another orange light appear next to it. Both faded out eventually. Both looked the same.
Summary: Saw an orange, star-like light move across the horizon abt. 45 deg, another appeared next to it,
trends: There have been 52 other sightings in Minneapolis
There were no other sightings in Minneapolis on or around June 1st 2012
